Hey! I think this could be useful 💁‍♀️ Next time you wanna paint a phone case, you should buy a see-through case. That way you can paint it on the inside and still see the design on the outside, making the same case the protective surface for the paint. I did it once using nail polish and it looked great 👌 The only precaution though is you'll have to put some kind of layer between the case and the phone, so the paint wouldn't stick... or maybe use like mate paint... or maybe just like a piece of paper 🤔

Well, hope this was helpful. I love your channel! You're hilarious! Byeeeeeeeeeeeeee ✌️🙃
